			section
				figure
					img(src="/static/talk/ai-slop-cycle-after.jpg")
					figcaption.
						Breaking the AI Slop Cycle
						
				aside.notes
					p AI is the vampire that requires fresh data. 

					p Which currently requires a human.
					
					p By specifying references for style, subjects and stories, artificial intelligence is permanently changing how we create and consume media.

			section
				h4 A good story transcends mediums
				aside.notes
					p Every person on earth can now become a creator and director of their very own worlds, materialising their imaginations into digital realms that give stories life and offer avenues for self-expression, exploration and art. 

